    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1941-05-02T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1941-05-02T00:00:00-05:00" n="670"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d670">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.51/7216</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chinese Ambassador</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hu Shih</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-05-02">May 2,
                            1941</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Under instructions of the Chinese Government I
                    have the honor to inform you that Dr. T. V. Soong has been duly appointed and
                    designated and is acting as agent, representative and attorney-in-fact of the
                    National Government of the Republic of China to act on behalf of the Government
                    in securing and receiving aid from the United States of America, or any agency
                    or instrumentality thereof, under the Lease-Lend Act of March 11, 1941.<note
                        n="57" xml:id="d670fn1">55 Stat. 31.</note>
                </p>
                <p>I shall be greatly obliged if you will be so good as to transmit the above
                    information to the appropriate branches of the United States Government.</p>
                <p>Accept [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hu Shih</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
